'''索尼影業駭客入侵事件'''是发生于2014年11月24日的一场[[駭客|駭客]]攻击事件。駭客组织“和平卫士”（Guardians of Peace）公布[[索尼影业|索尼影业]]员工[[电邮|电邮]]，涉及公司高管薪酬和索尼未发行[[电影|电影]][[拷贝|拷贝]]等内容<ref name=time>{{cite web | url=http://time.com/3633385/sony-hack-emails-media/ | title=Sony Asks Media to Stop Covering Hacked Emails | work=[[Time_(magazine)|Time]] | date=December 16, 2014 | accessdate=December 17, 2014 | archive-date=2016-07-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160723035244/http://time.com/3633385/sony-hack-emails-media/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/2014/12/17/sony-hack-the-interview/20519545/ | title=Experts: Sony hackers 'have crossed the line' | work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] | date=December 17, 2014 | accessdate=December 17, 2014 | author=Weise, Elizabeth}}</ref>。尽管[[美国|美国]]情报官员认为该網路攻击获得[[朝鲜政府|朝鲜政府]]资助，但就北韓是否得到索尼影业内部电脑技术员工的帮助仍存在分歧<ref name=nyt-linkedtokorea/> 。

尽管駭客的动机尚未透露，但行动与即将上映的电影《[[采访_(电影)|刺殺金正恩]]》有关，此片描绘了一起针对[[朝鲜最高领导人|朝鲜最高领导人]][[金正恩|金正恩]]的[[暗杀|暗杀]]行动；一旦此片发行，駭客扬言发动[[恐怖主义|恐怖主义]]行动。索尼影业一时计划取消此片的发行，但最終還是在[[耶誕節|耶誕節]]如期發行。

2015年1月8日，[[CNN|CNN]]報導稱，北韓秘密的駭客網路部隊北韓秘密的[[朝鮮人民軍第121局|駭客網路部隊121局]]在中国[[辽宁省|辽宁省]][[沈阳市|沈阳市]]設有秘密据點，[[七宝山饭店|七宝山饭店]]是北韓駭客活动的地點之一；而中方予以否認。<ref>{{Cite newspaper|url=http://world.huanqiu.com/exclusive/2015-01/5366924.html|title=记者探访美国所谓“朝鲜駭客”所在酒店|accessdate=2015-01-09|author=范凌志|date=2015-01-08|publisher=[[环球时报|环球时报]]|language=zh-cn}}</ref>

== 背景 ==
“和平卫士”曾多次扬言发动恐怖袭击，自[[九一一恐怖袭击|九一一恐怖袭击]]以来，已引起美国安全部门的注意<Ref name="bbc2"/>。朝鲜政府资助的黑客已涉嫌针对上映关于暗杀[[金正恩|金正恩]]的电影《采访》的影院，提出具体的威胁<ref name="variety cancelled"/><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.newsweek.com/did-north-korea-hack-sony-292050 | title=Did North Korea Hack Sony? | work=[[Newsweek|Newsweek]] | date=December 15, 2014 | accessdate=December 16, 2014 | author=Bennett, Bruce}}</ref>。朝鲜官员此前曾就影片对美国表示关注，指出“允许制作和分销暗杀[[主权国家|主权国家]]现任领导人的电影，应被视为[[恐怖主义|恐怖主义]]最为露骨的赞助，是战争行为”<Ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/jul/10/north-korea-un-the-interview-seth-rogen-james-franco | title = North Korea complains to UN about Seth Rogen comedy The Interview | first = Ben | last = Beaumont-Thomas | date = July 10, 2014 | accessdate = December 18, 2014 | work = [[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] }}</ref>。

12月17日，美国政府官员表示，他们最初小心朝鲜政府黑客“参与其中”，但白宫内部仍就是否正式指控朝鲜展开辩论<ref name=nyt-linkedtokorea>{{cite news|title=U.S. Links North Korea to Sony Hacking|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/18/world/asia/us-links-north-korea-to-sony-hacking.html?_r=0|accessdate=December 17, 2014|date=December 17, 2014| work = [[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | first1 = David E. | last1 = Sanger | first2 = Nicole | last2= Perlroth }}</ref>，白宫官员正处理“严重威胁国家安全”的局势<ref>{{Cite web | url =http://news-briefs.ew.com/2014/12/18/white-house-sony-interview-north-korea/ | title =  White House is treating Sony hack as 'serious national security matter' | work = [[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] | date = December 18, 2014 | accessdate = December 18, 2014 | first = Ariana | last = Bacle }}</ref>。人们建议采用类似的恶意黑客工具和技术，用韩国的机构跟朝鲜黑客连接，但官员承认攻击来自朝鲜以外的电脑<ref name="guardian 20141219">{{cite web | url=http://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2014/dec/19/north-korea-responsible-sony-hack-us-official | title=Sony cyber attack linked to North Korean government hackers, FBI says| work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | date=19 December 2014 | accessdate=19 December 2014}}</ref><ref name=nyt-linkedtokorea/>。12月19日，[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]表示已找到朝鲜政府与网络攻击的关联<Ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/2014/12/19/sony-the-interview-hackers-gop/20635449/ | title = FBI confirms North Korea behind Sony hack | first1 = Elizabeth | last1 = Weise | first2 = Kevin | last2= Johnson | work = [[USA_Today|USA Today]] | date = December 19, 2014 | accessdate = December 19, 2014 }}</ref> 。朝鲜拒绝承担责任<ref name=variety>{{cite web | url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/sony-hack-bond-producers-say-spectre-screenplay-among-stolen-material-1201379203/ | title=Sony Hack: Bond Producers Say 'Spectre' Screenplay Among Stolen Material | work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date=December 14, 2014 | accessdate=December 15, 2014 | author=Stedman, Alex}}</ref>，但表示朝鲜在全球范围内“有大量支持者和同情者”，有能力应付行动<Ref name="bbc2">{{cite web | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-30538154 | title = Sony hack: White House views attack as security issue | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] | date=  December 18, 2014 | accessdate = December 18, 2014 }}</ref>。

同时，美国知名网络情报公司“诺尔斯公司”（Norse Corporation）的官员们在与联邦调查局会面时表示，调查人员无法找到朝鲜“下令、策划或者资助了”这次袭击的迹象，同时认为袭击是由索尼公司一名心怀不满的前员工发动的；但联邦调查局在会面后坚称朝鲜應为袭击负责。<ref>[http://world.huanqiu.com/article/2015-01/5329092.html 美坚称朝黑客侵入索尼 私人调查人员称或内鬼所为]</ref>

根据《[[福布斯|福布斯]]》文章，早前2006年，索尼的网络曾被质疑存在安全问题，员工密码过于简单<ref>{{Cite web | url =http://www.forbes.com/sites/josephsteinberg/2014/12/11/massive-security-breach-at-sony-heres-what-you-need-to-know/ | title = Massive Security Breach At Sony -- Here's What You Need To Know | work = [[Forbes|Forbes]] | date=  December 9, 2014 | accessdate = December 18, 2014 | author=Joseph Steinberg |authorlink=Joseph Steinberg }}</ref>。2014年黑客公布的数据显示，索尼在2014年仍在使用这样的密码<ref>{{Cite web | url =http://www.csmonitor.com/Innovation/2014/1204/Trove-of-Sony-financial-data-passwords-movies-leaked-online | title = Trove of Sony financial data, passwords, movies leaked online | work = [[Christian_Science_Monitor|Christian Science Monitor]] | date=  December 4, 2014 | accessdate = December 18, 2014 | author=Jeff Ward Bailey}}</ref>。

== 获得的訊息及威胁 ==
根据电邮透露的信息，索尼CEO[[平井一夫|平井一夫]]向索尼影业联合董事长[[艾米·帕斯卡|艾米·帕斯卡]]施压，要求“淡化”计划上映的索尼电影《采访》的暗杀场面<ref name=nytimes>{{cite web | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/15/world/sonys-international-incident-making-kims-head-explode.html?_r=0 | title=Sony's International Incident: Making Kim Jong-un's Head Explode | work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]] | date=December 15, 2014 | accessdate=December 15, 2014 | author=Fackler, Martin}}</ref>。其他电邮显示帕斯卡跟[[斯科特·鲁丁|斯科特·鲁丁]]谈论[[安吉丽娜·朱莉|安吉丽娜·朱莉]]，朱莉想让[[大卫·芬奇|大卫·芬奇]]执导她的电影《克娄巴特拉》。在电邮中，鲁丁称朱莉“有点撒娇才华”，并称不想让她卷入正在策划的跟[[史蒂夫·乔布斯|史蒂夫·乔布斯]]有关的电影<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2014/dec/14/sony-pictures-email-hack-greed-racism-sexism | title=Sony email hack: what we've learned about greed, racism and sexism | work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | date=December 14, 2014 | accessdate=December 17, 2014 | author=Holpuch, Amanda}}</ref>。帕斯卡将自己将要跟[[美国总统|美国总统]][[奥巴马|奥巴马]]會面的消息透过电邮告诉鲁丁，电邮中奥巴马被称为“[[种族主义|种族主义]]者<ref name="mikefleming">Mike Fleming, Jr., [http://deadline.com/2014/12/scott-rudin-apology-sony-hacking-barack-obama-1201320321/ Scott Rudin Apologizes After Leak Of Sony’s Hacked Racially Insensitive E-Mails On Barack Obama], ''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]'', December 11, 2014</ref><ref name="varietyapologizes">Variety Staff, [http://variety.com/2014/film/news/sonys-amy-pascal-apologizes-for-obama-emails-not-who-i-am-1201377177/ Sony’s Amy Pascal Apologizes for Obama Emails], ''[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]'', December 11, 2014</ref><ref name="huffrosen">Christopher Rosen, [http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/12/11/scott-rudin-amy-pascal-apology_n_6310040.html Scott Rudin & Amy Pascal Apologize After Racially Insensitive Emails About Obama Leak], ''[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]'', December 11, 2014</ref>”；两人提议，应在跟奥巴马会面时，多提些[[非裔美国人|非裔美国人]]电影，如《[[被解放的姜戈|被解放的姜戈]]》、《[[为奴十二年|为奴十二年]]》、《[[白宫管家|白宫管家]]》和《[[勇者无惧|勇者无惧]]》等关于美国[[奴隶制|奴隶制]]和前民权时代电影<ref name="mikefleming"/>。帕斯卡和鲁丁随后出面道歉<ref name="varietyapologizes"/><ref name="huffrosen"/>。

黑客声称从索尼获得超过100TB的数据<ref>{{cite news |author=James Cook |date=December 16, 2014 |url=http://www.businessinsider.com/the-sony-hackers-still-have-a-massive-amount-of-data-that-hasnt-been-leaked-yet-2014-12 |title=Sony Hackers Have Over 100 Terabytes Of Documents. Only Released 200 Gigabytes So Far |work=[[Business_Insider|Business Insider]] |accessdate=December 18, 2014 |archive-date=2014-12-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217204735/http://www.businessinsider.com/the-sony-hackers-still-have-a-massive-amount-of-data-that-hasnt-been-leaked-yet-2014-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，泄露揭示了[[哥伦比亚影业|哥伦比亚影业]]目前大热门的[[蜘蛛侠系列电影|蜘蛛侠系列电影]]后台政治的多个细节，其中包括帕斯卡和[[漫威影业|漫威影业]]多位高管的电邮，意外揭示雙方對於蜘蛛人在[[漫威電影宇宙|漫威電影宇宙]]現身的談判。 <ref>{{cite news |last=Fritz |first=Ben |date=December 9, 2014 |url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2014/12/09/sony-marvel-discussed-spider-man-movie-crossover/ |title=Sony, Marvel Discussed Spider-Man Movie Crossover |work=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]] |accessdate=December 18, 2014 |archive-date=2014-12-11 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6Uk7cNMvQ?url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2014/12/09/sony-marvel-discussed-spider-man-movie-crossover/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。除了邮件，于2015年发行的[[詹姆斯·邦德系列电影|詹姆斯·邦德电影]]《[[大破魔鬼党|大破魔鬼党]]》的剧本复件被公布<ref name=variety/>。索尼影业未来的数部电影，包括《[[安妮：纽约奇缘|安妮：纽约奇缘]]》、《[[特纳先生|特纳先生]]》、《[[我想念我自己|我想念我自己]]》和《[[写爱于臂上|写爱于臂上]]》也被泄露<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/technology/2014/dec/04/north-korea-denies-hacking-sony-pictures-cyber-attack-movies|title=North Korea denies hacking Sony Pictures|author=Justin McCurry|work=the Guardian|accessdate=December 17, 2014}}</ref><ref name="guardian-invoke911">{{cite news|title=Hackers who targeted Sony invoke 9/11 attacks in warning to moviegoers|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/dec/16/employees-sue-failure-guard-personal-data-leaked-hackers|accessdate=December 17, 2014|work=The Guardian}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Sony's New Movies Leak Online Following Hack Attack|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/tech/tech-news/sonys-new-movies-leak-online-following-hack-attack-n258511|website=NBC News|accessdate=December 1, 2014|archive-date=2014-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141202203232/http://www.nbcnews.com/tech/tech-news/sonys-new-movies-leak-online-following-hack-attack-n258511|dead-url=no}}</ref>。黑客打算在2014年12月25日发布更多的信息，当天是已被取消的《采访》在美国发布的日子<ref name="usatoday">{{cite web | url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/2014/12/15/sony-hack-fbi-guardians-of-peace-meeting-christmas-hack/20364841/ | title=Sony fights hack damage as new threats emerge | work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] | date=December 15, 2014 | accessdate=December 15, 2014 | author=Weise, Elizabeth}}</ref>。

12月16日，黑客组织“和平卫士”率先提到《采访》，扬言要在12月18日要对影片在纽约阳光电影院的首映礼、以及12月25日全美上映日发动恐怖袭击<ref>{{cite news|last=Rushe|first=Dominic|title=Hackers who targeted Sony invoke 9/11 attacks in warning to moviegoers|url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2014/dec/16/employees-sue-failure-guard-personal-data-leaked-hackers|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|date=December 17, 2014|accessdate=December 18, 2014}}</ref>。索尼在翌日推迟影片的上映。

12月18日，两条据称来自“和平卫士”的消息被发布：一条是索尼高层的秘密消息，称不要发布电影，并将影片消息从互联网上删除；另一条在此前“和平卫士”用来发布消息的文本存储Web应用程序[[Pastebin|Pastebin]]发布，称片方「承受的够多了」，他们可能允许《采访》上映，尽管金正恩的死亡场面不太让人高兴。该帖子还指出，公司不能“再让他们当活靶子”，“若（索尼）走别的路，（他们）就要准备开战<ref>{{cite news |last1=Weise |first1=Elizabeth |last2=Johnson |first2=Kevin |title=FBI confirms North Korea behind Sony hack |url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/2014/12/19/sony-the-interview-hackers-gop/20635449/ |newspaper=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] |date=December 19, 2014 |accessdate=December 19, 2014}}</ref>。”

== 反应 ==
2014年12月，索尼要求媒体停止报道黑客攻击事件<ref name=time/>。若媒体不遵守，索尼将采取法律行动。但法学教授尤金·沃洛科（Eugene Volokh）认为，索尼的法律威胁“无效<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/volokh-conspiracy/wp/2014/12/15/can-sony-sue-media-outlets-who-publish-the-stolen-sony-documents/ | last = Volokh |first = Eugene | work = [[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]] | title = Can Sony sue media outlets who publish the stolen Sony documents? | date = December 15, 2014 | accessdate = December 15, 2014}}</ref>”。

出演电影的[[塞斯·罗根|塞斯·罗根]]和[[詹姆斯·弗兰科|詹姆斯·弗兰科]]回应黑客事件时，表示不知道电影是否是事件矛头<ref>{{cite web | url=http://abcnews.go.com/Entertainment/seth-rogen-james-franco-address-sony-hack/story?id=27609120 | title=Seth Rogen and James Franco Address the Sony Hack | publisher=[[ABC_News|ABC News]] | date=December 15, 2014 | accessdate=December 15, 2014}}</ref>，但后来取消了关于电影于2014年12月16日在纽约首映媒体见面会<ref name="variety cancelled">{{Cite web | url = http://variety.com/2014/film/news/seth-rogen-and-james-franco-cancel-all-media-appearances-for-the-interview-1201380917/ | title = Seth Rogen and James Franco Cancel All Media Appearances for 'The Interview' | first = Alex | last = Stedman | date=  December 16, 2014 | accessdate = December 16, 2014 | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] }}</ref>。美国编剧亚伦·索尔金曾在《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》撰写专栏，称媒体协助黑客发布和报道泄露的消息<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2014/12/15/opinion/aaron-sorkin-journalists-shouldnt-help-the-sony-hackers.html?_r=0 | title=The Sony Hack and the Yellow Press | work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] | date=December 15, 2014 | accessdate=December 16, 2014 | author=Sorkin, Aaron}}</ref>。奥巴马在年终记者会上谈到了索尼的黑客攻击事件，表示他认为索尼在拍片子时犯了个错误，制片方“不应被这种行为吓到<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-30548747 | title = US President Barack Obama holds last news briefing of 2014 | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] | date = December 19, 2014 | accessdate = December 19, 2014 }}</ref>”。为回应奥巴马总统的表态，索尼娱乐CEO迈克尔·林顿在[[CNN|CNN]]访谈节目《[[安德森·库珀|安德森·库珀360°]]》上表示，美国公众、媒体和奥巴马误解此事件。林顿表示，他们将另外处理未来电影的分销，并称“尚未放弃，而且并未退缩。我们一直有着让每位美国民众都能看这部电影的愿望<ref>{{cite web | last = Pallotta | first = Frank | date = December 19, 2014 | url  = http://money.cnn.com/2014/12/19/media/sony-executive-michael-lynton-responds-to-president-obama/index.html  | title = Sony exec fires back at President Obama | publisher = CNN Money | accessdate = December 19, 2014}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-30559169 | title = Sony 'will not drop' North Korea film The Interview | publisher = [[BBC|BBC]] | date = December 19, 2014 | accessdate = December 19, 2014 }}</ref>”。

遭到威胁的上映《采访》的院线有[[卡米克影院|卡米克影院]]（Carmike Cinemas）、[[领带影院|领带影院]]（Bow Tie Cinemas）、[[富豪娱乐集团|富豪娱乐集团]]（Regal Entertianment Group）、[[AMC电影院|AMC电影院]]和[[喜满客影城|喜满客影城]]，都宣布不上映《采访》<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/sony-hack-carmike-cinemas-drops-758444 | title=Sony Hack: Carmike Cinemas Drops 'The Interview' | work=[[Hollywood_Reporter|Hollywood Reporter]] | date=December 16, 2014 | accessdate=December 17, 2014 | author=Kilday, Gregg}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/tech/2014/12/17/sony-hack-the-interview/20519545/ | title=Second theater chain pulls "The Interview" after hacker threats | work=USA Today | date=December 17, 2014 | accessdate=December 17, 2014 | author=Weise, Elizabeth}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Kilday|first1=Gregg|title=Top Five Theater Circuits Drop 'The Interview' After Sony Hack|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/source-top-five-theater-circuits-758843|accessdate=December 17, 2014|publisher=The Hollywood Reporter|date=December 17, 2014}}</ref>。同日，索尼表示允许院方下架《采访》，但后来决定电影于12月25日在全美铺开上映，并宣布家庭录影等平台“未有进一步的发行计划<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/sony-cancels-interview-new-york-premiere-amid-terror-threats-20141217 | title = Sony Cancels 'Interview' New York Premiere Amid Terror Threats | work = [[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] | date = December 17, 2014 | accessdate = December 17, 2014 | first = Kory | last = Grow }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://variety.com/2014/film/news/sony-cancels-theatrical-release-for-the-interview-on-christmas-1201382032/ | title = Sony Cancels Theatrical Release for 'The Interview' on Christmas | work = [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] | date = December 17, 2014 | accessdate = December 17, 2014 | first = Brent | last = Lang }}</ref><ref name="vod">{{cite news|work=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|date=December 17, 2014|accessdate=December 17, 2014|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/sony-has-no-further-release-plans-for-the-interview-1201382167/|title=Sony Has 'No Further Release Plans' for 'The Interview'|author= Dave McNary}}</ref>”。铺开发行影片招致包括[[本·斯蒂勒|本·斯蒂勒]]、[[史蒂夫·加瑞尔|史蒂夫·加瑞尔]]、[[罗伯·劳|罗伯·劳]]、[[吉米·坎摩尔|吉米·坎摩尔]]和[[贾德·阿帕托|贾德·阿帕托]]在内的好莱坞制片人和演员的批评<ref name=Reuters>{{cite news|last1=Sinha-Roy|first1=Piya|title=Hollywood slams Sony, movie theaters for canceling 'The Interview'|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/12/18/us-sony-cybersecurity-hollywood-idUSKBN0JW08W20141218|publisher=Reuters|date=Dec 17, 2014|accessdate=December 18, 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Marcus|first1=Stephanie|title=Celebrities React To Sony Canceling 'The Interview' Release|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/12/17/celebrities-react-the-interview-canceled_n_6344232.html|publisher=Huffington Post|date=December 7, 2014|accessdate=December 18, 2014|archive-date=2014-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141218111029/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2014/12/17/celebrities-react-the-interview-canceled_n_6344232.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。有评论家将情况对比2004年无争议上映的讥讽朝鲜前领导人[[金正日|金正日]]的《[[美国战队：世界警察|美国战队：世界警察]]》<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.avclub.com/article/alamo-drafthouse-replaces-interview-team-america-w-213181 | title = UPDATED: Alamo Drafthouse replaces The Interview with Team America: World Police—or not | first = Katie | last= Rife | date = December 18, 2014 | accessdate = December 18, 2014 | publisher = [[A.V._Club|A.V. Club]] }}</ref>。阿拉莫影院准备将《采访》换成《美国战队》，直至影片的发行商[[派拉蒙|派拉蒙]]下禁令<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.mercurynews.com/movies-dvd/ci_27159719/paramount-tells-theaters-no-team-america | title = Paramount tells theaters no 'Team America: World Police' | first = Donovan | last = Farnham | date = December 18, 2014 | accessdate = December 18, 2014 | work = [[San_Jose_Mercury_News|San Jose Mercury News]] }}</ref>。

由于索尼制作《采访》时的威胁，[[摄政娱乐公司|摄政娱乐公司]]取消其2015年3月制作基于漫画小说《[[平壤_(漫画)|平壤]]》的计划，该电影由[[史蒂夫·加瑞尔|史蒂夫·加瑞尔]]主演<ref>{{Cite web | url =http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/steve-carells-north-korea-thriller-758901 | title = Steve Carell's North Korea Thriller Dropped After Sony Hack | work = [[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] | date=  December 17, 2014 | accessdate = December 17, 2014 | first = Rebecca | last = Ford }}</ref>。

2014年12月19日，[[人權觀察|人權觀察]]亞洲宣傳總監约翰·希福顿号召好莱坞反制朝鲜政府的威脅。在他的评论中，希福頓写道：“如果好莱坞震驚於上一週發生的狀況，他们应该借他们日漸上升的名望努力使联合国提高对[[朝鮮民主主義人民共和國人權|朝鲜人权]]現况的關注。”。<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.hrw.org/news/2014/12/19/hollywood-should-take-stand-human-rights-north-korea | title = Hollywood Should Take a Stand on Human Rights in North Korea | publisher = [[Human_Rights_Watch|Human Rights Watch]] | date = December 19, 2014 | accessdate = December 24, 2014}}</ref>

